</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3E4936F7FF90FF930DB81D00FC8EC8B8" blockId="9.[151,1437,1878,2013]" pageId="9" pageNumber="370">
<emphasis id="0C82EAE5FF90FF930DB81D00FE82C8F0" box="[199,264,1915,1941]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="370">Color</emphasis>
. Body dark castaneous, metasoma castaneous. Mandible castaneous with teeth yellowish-brown. Antenna yellow to yellowish-brown. Legs castaneous, trochanters, tibiae and tarsi yellow. Forewing hyaline tinged with yellowish; veins and pterostigma light castaneous.
</paragraph>
