<quantity id="F90E9B12FF95FF960CA419A8FD08CC88" box="[475,642,979,1005]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.495" metricValueMax="3.73" metricValueMin="3.26" pageId="12" pageNumber="373" unit="mm" value="3.495" valueMax="3.73" valueMin="3.26">3.26–3.73 mm</quantity>
. Length of forewing: 
<quantity id="F90E9B12FF95FF960E0319A8FBA9CC88" box="[892,1059,979,1005]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.11" metricValueMax="2.28" metricValueMin="1.94" pageId="12" pageNumber="373" unit="mm" value="2.11" valueMax="2.28" valueMin="1.94">1.94–2.28 mm</quantity>
. LH 1.11–1.19 × WH; WF 1.13– 1.48 × LE; LE 0.95–1.02 × DEV; POL 1.05–1.27 × AOL; OOL 2.23–2.81 × WOT; DPV 1.12–1.53 × DAO.
</paragraph>
